==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncamp
<hw>Un*camp"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>camp</ets>.]</ety> <def>To break up the camp of;
to dislodge from camp.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If they could but now <qex>uncamp</qex> their enemies.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncanny</ent>⟦br⟧
